You feel a surge. The hum of electrical power reverberates through the facility. Halogen tubes flicker on, irradiating its sterile corridors with artificial light, rendering surfaces of gleaming metal and glass. Electrons trace out their synaptic pathways. The mainframe responds. You race ahead as the clock runs out, following an electric flow in the dark.
